lead_paragraph: Megan Podkowa and Jessica January each scored 16 points to help No. 24 DePaul beat Creighton 81-63 on Friday night for its fourth straight win in the series.

headline.print_headline: Podkowa, January Lead No. 24 DePaul Women by Creighton 81-63
